rows.label: qst103409_msg0001
rows.name: Is there something you want to discuss?

rows.label: qst103409_msg0002
rows.name:
What? You defeated Akatsuki and
his Driver? Are you certain?

rows.label: qst103409_msg0003
rows.name:
A Core Crystal...
This is Akatsuki's?

rows.label: qst103409_msg0004
rows.name:
Would it be all right if I kept hold
of this? As evidence, you understand.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0006
rows.name:
With this, I suppose the anti-imperialist
schemes of Brionac really are finished.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0008
rows.name:
Lindwurm...
I'm sorry, I can't say I've ever
heard the name before.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0009
rows.name:
Of course, it may not be wise to take
everything Akatsuki said at face value.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0010
rows.name:
There was that time when he
taunted you with empty threats
before letting you leave, after all.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0011
rows.name:
At any rate, thank you for all the work
you've done in service of the Empire.

rows.label: qst103409_msg0012
rows.name:
We can handle the task of rounding
up any remaining stray rebels, so don't
worry yourselves any further.
